metadata.name: JED XO - Choices
metadata.description: "Choices" is a powerful and introspective song that explores the theme of personal responsibility and decision-making. The lyrics encourage listeners to take ownership of their choices, to learn from their mistakes, and to focus on self-improvement. The track features JED's trademark confident and self-assured style, with a catchy hook and compelling verses that showcase his lyrical prowess. Produced by Matthew Cummings, "Choices" is a testament to the collaborative and innovative potential of blockchain music, and is sure to resonate with fans of JED XO's sound and message
